reviews.text: Standard, Starbucks - friendly folks, good coffee, good location, comfortable seats.
Wonderful coffee great service great cakes

The service is fast as Starbucks standard. Plenty of choices of bread and cake. Yet, no table with wall power socket. I didn't try to ask but it seems there's no publicly available toilet. You got WiFi access but only for 30 mins.

Starbucks. Am I in New York? Taipei? London? I just don't know. A larger location though with ample seating and above average friendly and helpful staff that during my visit at least spoke English. Air conditioned.
Whenever I'm away overseas I use Starbucks coffee shops to buy my coffee I enjoy it
